{"actor":"ydeng11","comment":null,"created_at":"2026-03-01T23:08:34Z","event_type":"claimed","id":417,"issue_id":"minance2-nt1","new_value":"{\"assignee\":\"ydeng11\",\"status\":\"in_progress\"}","old_value":"{\"id\":\"minance2-nt1\",\"title\":\"Transactions filter bug: stale category param when switching granular-\\u003ecoarse\",\"description\":\"When category filter is set in granular mode (e.g. Dining), switching Category View to coarse and applying filters sends GET /v1/transactions?category=Dining\\u0026category_view=coarse. This stale granular category is invalid for coarse mode and returns empty rows until filters are applied again after category resets to All. Repro captured in docs/transactions-tab-parity-inventory.md and output/playwright/parity/minance2-xdy.2/coarse-stale-filter.snapshot.yml. Expected: mode switch should clear/translate incompatible category before issuing coarse-mode query.\",\"status\":\"open\",\"priority\":1,\"issue_type\":\"bug\",\"owner\":\"eugene.deng2077@gmail.com\",\"created_at\":\"2026-03-02T04:07:15Z\",\"created_by\":\"ydeng11\",\"updated_at\":\"2026-03-02T04:07:15Z\"}"}
